doc_summary_long: Health officials in San Francisco say the drink contained the plant-based toxin aconite, causing life-threatening heart rhythms Two people have been hospitalised in San Francisco after drinking tea from the same Chinatown herbalist. The city's public health department said on Friday that the tea leaves bought at Sun Wing Wo Trading Company contained the plant-based toxin aconite.
doc_summary_short: Health officials in San Francisco say the drink contained the plant-based toxin aconite, causing life-threatening heart rhythms
doc_title: Two people critically ill after drinking toxic herbal tea
